
####################
##   Python 3.x  ###
####################

##first run pip to install the module

pip install -r requirements.txt


## next run this to create database
python3 scrap/script/create_database.py


## next migrate the server

python3 manage.py makemigrations
python3 manage.py migrate


##lastly run the server

python3 manage.py runserver



If you have a request to add something, dont hesitate to pull a request...